title: Zillow Neighborhood Boundaries, California
name: Zillow Neighborhood Boundaries, California
description: This is a reference boundary file of various neighborhoods in major cities of California. The cities included are: Anaheim, Bakersfield, Chula Vista, Davis, Fremont, Fresno, Glendale, Hayward, Irvine, Long Beach, Los Angeles, Oakland, Palo Alto, Pasadena, Riverside, Sacramento, San Bernardino, San Diego, San Francisco, San Jose, San Mateo, Santa Ana, Santa Barbara, Stockton, and Torrance. The data comes from Zillow and was obtained on 2.8.2010.
